organic_results.title: Organizational factors that affect school sense of efficacy, community, and expectations
organic_results.snippet: This study contends that the alienation of teachers in high schools can be reduced through improvements in school organization. Using the High School and Beyond Administrator/Teacher Survey, the study explored the impact of 10 organizational features on efficacy, community, and expectations in 353 public high schools.
